race.comment: BOURBON COUNTY (5) was heavily supported on debut and didn't let supporters down with a solid win at the Sunny Coast. Was then tipped out for further time to furnish and has since tuned up for this with a recent trial victory. Rates the testing material. ROYAL MOVER (4) got the maiden out of the way over this sprint trip when facing the starter for the first time and gets Maloney on board from the favourable draw. Can go right on with the job now. BEFORE ANYONE ELSE (8) resumes here but the form she showed in her first preparation was up to the mark for a race of this calibre. Top-three credentials while fresh. MANPOWER (2) has gone bang bang to start the campaign and gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim. In the mix. CERTIFIED COPY (1) rounds out the selections.
